Title: Advanced Project Management and Strategic Leadership (APMSL)
Discription: Advanced Project Management and Strategic Leadership is divided into modules which will include application of knowledge, tools & techniques necessary to implement projects. The program will cover various body of knowledge in project management implemented globally. As a Project Leader you will learn managing stakeholders and uncertainty, building relationship for a value based project outcome. The program is designed to improve your knowledge and skills and make help you grow as Strategic Leader for decision making in project based environment
